	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Thu, Dec 7th 8:17 AM 2000</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>I was wondering if anyone could suggest some good healing hotkeys.&nbsp;&nbsp;I know that when I'm fighting, and need to heal myself, I have to press A, target myself, heal, target the enemy, then press A again.  Most times by then, the enemy has done enough damage to me to totally have negated anything I had just healed.  I was hoping someone had a simple list of commands I could put into a hotkey to make things faster and hopefully more efficient.  Thanks for any imput.<br><br>Jacqui of the Tattered Wings 9th level<br>Rathe Server<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
