<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=97951104922497></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f97951104922497><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=7&mid=97951104922497>RE: Healing HotKeys</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=7&mid=97951104922497#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=13884><span id= >Mendan</span></a>, <span id= > </span><br><span id=notbold>38 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Sun, Jan 14th 10:26 PM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2> I set up my functions keys so that F1=me, F2=closest NPC, F3 and greater is group menbers.&nbsp;&nbsp;Set up your heal spell in hotkey 3.  Then hit F1, 3, F2.  You'll cast on yourself and retarget the enemy.  Just watch out if you have more than on NPC attacking you, it's possible to target the wrong one.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
